WEBVTT

00:00:00.793 --> 00:00:02.967
Zelim da na trenutak

00:00:03.030 --> 00:00:06.197
zamislite igru monopola,

00:00:07.274 --> 00:00:09.424
u kojoj su kombinacija

00:00:09.424 --> 00:00:12.393
vjestine, talenta i srece,

00:00:12.393 --> 00:00:14.931
koji inace, kao i u zivotu, znace pobjedu,

00:00:14.931 --> 00:00:16.347
ucinjeni beznacajnim,

00:00:16.347 --> 00:00:18.642
zato sto je igra namjestena,

00:00:18.642 --> 00:00:20.522
a vi imate prednost.

00:00:20.522 --> 00:00:22.401
Imate vise novaca,

00:00:22.401 --> 00:00:24.961
vise mogucnosti da se krecete po tabli,

00:00:24.961 --> 00:00:27.186
i pristup vecem broju sredstava.

00:00:27.186 --> 00:00:28.517
I dok razmisljate o ovom iskustvu,

00:00:28.517 --> 00:00:31.105
zelim da se zapitate